There's two parts
there's the Motivation. I describe the problem and give you a reason to want to do anything at all
Which involves some Background
Then the Program. I tell you what you'll have to do. For example, start conflicts
Then I also tell you stuff you'll need to do to mitigate that. For example, be ruthlessly positive

the program is about something that everyone has experienced every single day of their lives: dealing with people
so what can i possibly offer?
1. breaking down misconceptions
2. building new ways of understanding
